PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1773436323
OL,3,CRachel Reeves asks watchdog to 'crack
OL,4,Cdown' on fuel 'rip-offs' amid Iran war
OL,6,FThe Government has already promised to
OL,7,Fintervene if companies engage in
OL,8,F"unfair" practices that would hit
OL,9,Fcustomers facing a rise in the price
OL,10,Fof home heating oil, which is not
OL,11,Fcovered by Ofgem's energy price cap.
OL,13,FThe Treasury has said Ms Reeves and
OL,14,FEnergy Secretary Ed Miliband will also
OL,15,Fpress petrol retailers and energy
OL,16,Fsuppliers to ensure drivers are not
OL,17,Fleft paying "over the odds" in a
OL,18,FDowning Street meeting on Friday.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@HO]yD@MOUyD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1773436323
OL,3,CRachel Reeves asks watchdog to 'crack
OL,4,Cdown' on fuel 'rip-offs' amid Iran war
OL,6,FAhead of the talks, the Chancellor
OL,7,Fwrote to the Competition and Markets
OL,8,FAuthority (CMA) requesting it to stay
OL,9,Fon "high alert" for "unjustifiable"
OL,10,Fprice hikes, the ministry said.
OL,12,F"I will not tolerate any company
OL,13,Fexploiting the current situation to
OL,14,Fmake excess profits at consumers'
OL,15,Fexpense. I'm backing drivers and
OL,16,Ffamilies ` and I expect a fair deal at
OL,17,Fthe pump," Ms Reeves said.
OL,26,@qD@DOUqD@OO]qD@UOUqD@cO]tD@AOUyD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
