OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1773436323
OL,3,CRachel Reeves asks watchdog to 'crack
OL,4,Cdown' on fuel 'rip-offs' amid Iran war
OL,6,FHowever, the AA warned that consumers
OL,7,F"will be stung" with inevitable rising
OL,8,Fcosts because of a global hike in
OL,9,Fprices, and called on Ms Reeves to
OL,10,Fdelay a planned increase in fuel duty.
OL,12,FThe Chancellor has faced opposition
OL,13,Fpressure to abandon her decision to
OL,14,Fgradually phase out a 5p cut to the
OL,15,Flevy, starting with a 1p increase from
OL,16,FSeptember this year.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
