SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1773436323
OL,3,CRachel Reeves asks watchdog to 'crack
OL,4,Cdown' on fuel 'rip-offs' amid Iran war
OL,6,FEdmund King, president of the motoring
OL,7,Forganisation, said: "As the conflict
OL,8,Fin the Middle East continues, the
OL,9,Fglobal increase in oil prices will
OL,10,Fhurt inflation, particularly with the
OL,11,Fdiesel price hikes.
OL,13,F"As most goods and services are
OL,14,Fdelivered by diesel vehicles, this
OL,15,Fwill lead to price rises which the
OL,16,Fconsumer will be stung with.
OL,26,@oD@UOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
