FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1773436323
OL,3,CRachel Reeves asks watchdog to 'crack
OL,4,Cdown' on fuel 'rip-offs' amid Iran war
OL,6,F"We strongly encourage the Chancellor
OL,7,Fto delay the staggered reintroduction
OL,8,Fof the 5p fuel duty discount in order
OL,9,Fto offer some breathing space for hard-
OL,10,Fpressed households."
OL,12,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer has
OL,13,Fsince said the Government will keep
OL,14,Fthe situation "under review" in light
OL,15,Fof the Middle East conflict.
OL,17,FIt comes after the CMA warned it was
OL,18,Fputting fuel retailers "on notice" of
OL,19,Fplans to step up monitoring of petrol
OL,20,Fand diesel prices in light of the
OL,21,FMiddle East conflict.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@TO]vD@OOUvD@\O]zD@XOUzD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
