OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1773436323
OL,3,CRachel Reeves asks watchdog to 'crack
OL,4,Cdown' on fuel 'rip-offs' amid Iran war
OL,6,FThe watchdog told firms it was
OL,7,Fbringing forward formal requirements
OL,8,Fto supply revenue, costs and sales
OL,9,Fdata.
OL,11,FThe CMA said it will also consider how
OL,12,Fquickly fuel prices rise and fall as
OL,13,Fwholesale costs change and whether
OL,14,Fthere is evidence of so-called rocket
OL,15,Fand feather pricing.
OL,17,FOn Wednesday, the RAC said diesel
OL,18,Fprices had risen by nearly 9% since
OL,19,FFebruary 28.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
