OL,3,CRachel Reeves asks watchdog to 'crack
OL,4,Cdown' on fuel 'rip-offs' amid Iran war
OL,6,FPetrol prices were on average 6% more
OL,7,Facross the same period.
OL,9,FThe Government has said drivers can
OL,10,Fcompare prices at different petrol
OL,11,Fstations across the UK through its
OL,12,Ffuel finder scheme, which has also
OL,13,Fbeen welcomed by the AA.
OL,15,FMr Miliband said: "Tackling the cost
OL,16,Fof living is our number one priority `
OL,17,Fall fuel retailers must sign up for
OL,18,Ffuel finder so drivers can find the
OL,19,Fcheapest price at the pump.
OL,26,@wD@SOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
