CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1773436323
OL,3,CRachel Reeves asks watchdog to 'crack
OL,4,Cdown' on fuel 'rip-offs' amid Iran war
OL,6,F"We will not hesitate to act to
OL,7,Fprotect consumers against any unfair
OL,8,Fpractices."
OL,10,FThe Tories said the Chancellor had the
OL,11,Fpower to ease the cost of living with
OL,12,Fpolicy changes but was failing to act.
OL,14,FShadow transport secretary Richard
OL,15,FHolden said: "She could cancel the
OL,16,Ffuel duty rise, she could cut the
OL,17,Ftaxes piled on to energy, she could
OL,18,Fstop piling costs on to the price of
OL,19,Ffuel ` but she isn't doing anything
OL,20,Fbecause she doesn't have the backbone.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@KO]wD@NOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
